<td style="border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid;" valign="middle">
<p><b>Rojo</b></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid;" valign="middle">
<p>Blanco</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr valign="top">
<td style="border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid;" valign="middle">
<p><b>Amarillo o amarillo anaranjado</b></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 1px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid;" valign="middle">
<p>Negro</p>
</td>
